text: Tambacounda is a region in the southeast of Senegal. The regional capital is Tambacounda. As of the 2013 census, 681,310 people lived there. It has an area of . == Départements == There are four départements: * Bakel Département * Goudiry Département * Koumpentoum Département * Tambacounda Département Category:Regions of Senegal
